Class UncontrollableReadableByteChannelMaster

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vanillasource.aio.channel.UncontrollableReadableByteChannelMaster
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AioMaster, ReadableByteChannelMaster, Closeable, AutoCloseable, Channel, ReadableByteChannel

    public final class UncontrollableReadableByteChannelMaster
extends Object
implements ReadableByteChannelMaster
    A channel leader that can not be controlled. Use only in cases where the follower can process the onReady() call completely on first call.
